title: New YouTube Upload.

embed.description: Just watch my health. FOR THOSE WHO DON'T UNDERSTAND: After killing Talon and suffering from his bleed, I realise that I'm going to die from the DoT if I don't do something. Knowing this, I place a ward down and Shunpo to it, reducing damage taken by 15% for 1.5 seconds.

body: Would really appreciate people checking it out. If you like it then check out my other vids as well. Feedback accepted.
